rComments: Sweetest teacher! She's caring and she is very passionate about her field of work. She is one of my favourite profs that i've ever had in my 4 year at uni. Even if the class material can be boring, she makes up for it with her good sense of humour. If you can, you should definitely take a PED class with her.

A very sweet lady that truly cares about her students. She is also really passionate about teaching and will make you want to become a better teacher. Only cons to this class is that theres a final group project worth 40% of your grade and that presence is mandatory (if youre absent, you need to advise her and bring a medical paper)
3 projects all year, final one was a group project presentation worth 40%
